<h1>Your Payment Has Been Rejected</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p>
  We regret to inform you that your payment for the task titled "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" has been rejected.
</p>

<p><strong>Payment Details:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Task:</strong> <%= @task.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ") %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @payment.status.titleize %></li>
</ul>

<p>
  We encourage you to review the task details and contact our support team if you require further clarification or assistance.
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your understanding. We value your work on GigHive and are here to assist you with any questions.
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The GigHive Team</p>
